[[File:3rd Age Druidic robes equipped.png|right|200px]]
'''3rd age druidic robes''' are a set of [[3rd age equipment]]. The robes require level 65 [[Prayer]] to wear. Players can obtain 3rd age druid robes equipment through [[Clue scroll (master)|master]] [[Treasure Trails]]; they cannot be bought in stores nor made through the [[Crafting]] skill.

Unlike its ''RuneScape'' counterpart, the 3rd age druidic wreath does not exist in ''Old School RuneScape''. This is due to the [[druidic wreath]], a reward from [[midsummer event]]s, already existing.

